<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>draw the badger • overdraw one’s badger</xh5><p> <i>draw the badger—</i>provoke a person to reveal his thoughts, etc.: The Parnellite taunts regarding Balfour’s indifference have at last <u>drawn the badger</u>.</p><p> <i>overdraw one’s badger</i>—(dated sl., in humorous reference to the above) overdraw one’s banking account: His checks no longer drew the cash.... He had <u>overdrawn his badger</u>.</p> </entry>
